  <brief_title>Combination Chemotherapy With or Without Rituximab in Treating Participants With Stage III-IV Classic Hodgkin Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase II Study of Rituximab With ABVD Versus Standard ABVD for Patients With Advanced-Stage Classical Hodgkin Lymphoma With Poor Risk Features (IPS Score &amp;gt; 2)</official_title>
